
This dataset contains gameplay training data collected from a full playthrough of Episode 1, Maps 1–6, with all levels completed successfully.


### Gameplay Style

The game was played carefully and vigilantly to help the model learn:

- How to move through maps efficiently
- How to explore corners and hidden areas
- How to return from dead ends and navigate back correctly
- How to search for exits and progression paths
- How to survive while exploring
- Combat behavior against monsters encountered during exploration
- Map completion behavior


The player intentionally explored different sections of the maps thoroughly so the model can better understand where important locations, exits, and pathways are usually found.

### Dataset Contents

Current dataset includes:

Episode 1; Maps 1-6
Fully completed levels
Combat interactions using bullets and shells
Exploration and navigation data
Exit-search behavior
User: user1 (Saman Fatima)

